<concept id="id_1" class="- topic/topic concept/concept "><title class="- topic/title ">Before you begin</title><conbody class="- topic/body  concept/conbody "><p class="- topic/p "><ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> is simple and easy to use, even for users without much programming and scripting experience. If you are new to <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/> but have some basic Java and/or Groovy skills and a brief understanding of testing, then you should have no problem making use of this tool.</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li ">To start, first, you need to verify if your computer meets the <xref href="../../../../General_Information/Supported_Environments/Supported_Environments_For_Katalon_Studio/supported-environments.dita" class="- topic/xref ">System Requirements</xref> of <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/>.</li><li class="- topic/li ">For how to install and set up <ph conkeyref="name-variables/katalon-studio" class="- topic/ph "/>, see <xref href="../../../../Get_Started/Katalon_Studio_Installation/Installation_Overview.dita" class="- topic/xref "/>.</li></ul></conbody></concept>